          "summary": "Backend API: Products and Cart endpoints",
          "description": "Implement FastAPI backend with in-memory storage. Endpoints: GET /health, CRUD for /products/, and /cart/ endpoints (add, clear, checkout, get cart). Use Pydantic v2 models. Configure CORS to allow all origins.",
